            . I took the prisoner on the 18th of March, about seven o'clock - I found on him this duplicate of the dial.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never had it in my possession, nor saw it before - this prosecutor was convicted here himself twelve months ago.</p>
